quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,90,"Ndithudi Aroni adawauza iwo poyamba kuti, “Oh Anthu anga! Inu muli kungoyesedwa nacho ichi koma, ndithudi, Ambuye wanu ndiye Mwini chisoni chosatha motero tsatireni ine ndipo mverani malamulo anga.”"
  20,91,"Iwo adati, “Ife sitidzasiya kuchipembedza ichi mpaka pamene Mose adza kwa ife.”"
  20,92,"Mose adati, “oh Aroni! Kodi chidakuletsa ndi chiyani kuwatsutsa iwo pamene udaona kuti ali kusochera?”"
  20,93,“Kuti siunanditsatire ine. Kodi waswa lamulo langa?”
  20,94,"Aroni adati, “Mwana wa Amayi anga! Usandikoke ndevu zanga kapena tsitsi langa! Ndithudi! Ine ndidali ndi mantha kuti mwina iwe ukhoza kudzanena kuti, iwe wabzala mpatuko pakati pa ana a Israyeli ndipo siunalemekeze mau anga.”"
  20,95,"Mose adati, “Iwe Msamiri, kodi chifukwa chiyani udachita izi?”"
  20,96,"Iye adati, “Ine ndidaona zimene iwo sanali kuona. Motero ine ndidatenga dothi lodzala m’manja kuchokera ku fumbi lochokera ku phazi la Mtumwi ndi kulitaya. Kotero mzimu wanga udandikakamiza.”"
  20,97,"Mose adati, “Choka! Ndithudi chilango chako m’moyo uno ndi chakuti udzanena kuti, ‘Musandikhudze.’ Ndithudi iwe uli ndi lonjezo limene siliphwanyidwa ayi. Taona mulungu wako amene wamutumikira ndi mtima wako wonse. Ife tidzaliotcha m’moto ndipo tidzamwaza phulusa lake pa nyanja.”"
  20,98,Mulungu wanu ndi Mulungu mmodzi yekha. Iye amadziwa chilichonse
  20,99,Kotero Ife tili kukufotokozerani mbiri ya zinthu zimene zidachitika kale. Ndithudi takupatsa chikumbutso
  20,100,Iwo amene adzachikana ndithudi adzanyamula katundu wolemera wamachimo pa tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa
  20,101,Iwo adzakhala m’menemo mpaka kalekale ndipo zidzakhala zoipa kwambiri kwa iwo osenza katundu wotereyu tsiku la kuuka kwa kufa
  20,102,"Tsiku limene lipenga lidzaimbidwa, patsiku limene Ife tidzasonkhanitsa anthu onse ochimwa, maso awo adzakhala obiriwira ndi nkhope zakuda"
  20,103,"Monong’onezana adzakhala ali nkuyankhulana nati, “Inu simunakhale padziko lapansi kupatula masiku khumi okha.”"
  20,104,"Ife tili kudziwa kwambiri zimene adzayankhula, pamene anthu awo angwiro ndi anzeru adzati, “Inu simunakhale padziko kupatula tsiku limodzi lokha.”"